{"tid":812974,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C.朗拿度趣事遭爆料：裸身對著鏡子自戀+犀利調侃美斯","createTime":"2018-09-10T05:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T06:58:34.000Z","uid":20634,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e36732caf45e974fd175550922a41194bd05a313","tid":812974,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/09/09/a/a07a4ecc6911c5df2930cced4befb66a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2Fa%2Fa07a4ecc6911c5df2930cced4befb66a.jpg&h=36f3d1ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現《每日郵報》專欄作家高治<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　前英格蘭著名高佬高治目前是英國媒體《每日郵報》的專欄作家，他也推出了關於自傳的書籍。而高治在他的專欄中透露了一件關於C.朗拿度的趣事。<br />\n<br />\n　　高治：「里奧-里奧費迪南告訴我，基斯坦奴-朗拿度會赤身裸體地站在鏡子前，用手輕撫自己的頭髮，然後說：<span style=\"color: red;\">哇，我實在是太帥了</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「而這個時候其他曼聯球員會上前調侃他：&lsquo;隨你吧，<span style=\"color: red;\">不過美斯是一個比你更強的球員哦</span>。&rsquo;這個時候C.朗拿度會聳聳肩，然後微笑地說道：&lsquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">是啊</span>，但美斯可沒我帥&rsquo;。」"},{"pid":"40f48eb1c86f7280457abf54ae77ac601f19fbc8","tid":812974,"uid":117187,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:27:10.000Z","msg":"J自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dcfc687c2879000caeee39d5c427b65b146e67","tid":812974,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:36:40.000Z","msg":"如果我操到c朗咁靚<br />\n我都會日日對住鏡打飛機j自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca559e7905952d1036189fc27819bdc109e11a41","tid":812974,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"唔知呢度有無巴打會對住C朗張相打飛機再射落佢到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69069b3f497434faae3f4461563c29cefae8ba8c","tid":812974,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply